    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1934-11-09T05:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1934-11-09T05:00:00-05:00" n="449"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d449">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">701.6593/30: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Italy</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Kirk</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Rome</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-11-09T11:00:00+01:00"
                            >November 9, 1934—11 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received November 9—6:34 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>246. Embassy’s despatch 748 of October 11th<note n="87" xml:id="d449fn87">Not
                        printed.</note> and previous correspondence. The appointment of Lojacono,
                    Italian Ambassador to Turkey, as Ambassador to China is announced today.<note
                        n="88" xml:id="d449fn88">Vincenzo Lojacono presented his credentials at
                        Nanking on January 25, 1935 (893.00 P. R. Nanking/84).</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kirk</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
